        	<div class="clear"></div>
            
			<div class="h2"><h2>Commercial Refrigeration Suppliers & Specialists</h2></div>
            <div>
            
            
 

 
 <p>Commercial Refrigeration Suppliers, Refrigeration Freezers are one of the UK's leading suppliers of commercial refrigeration equipment. Refrigeration Freezers was founded as part of the Foodmaster Refrigeration Group in the early 1970's, as freezers were the 'latest craze' and families bought them in bulk to save time and money. </p>
 
 <p>Since then we have gone on to be one of the most reputable refrigeration freezer suppliers for the hospitality industry with high-quality commercial <a href="http://www.refrigeration-freezers.com/commercial-refrigeration/storage-freezers/4/"> storage freezers</a>, <a href="http://www.refrigeration-freezers.com/commercial-refrigeration/display-fridges/1/">display fridges</a> and <a href="http://www.refrigeration-freezers.com/commercial-refrigeration/catering-displays/39/"> catering equipment</a> being supplied and installed to reputable, bars, clubs, restaurants, pubs, delicatessens &amp; convenience stores throughout UK.</p>
 
<div class="h2"><h2>Commercial Refrigeration Fitters &amp; Installers</h2></div>

 <p>Refrigeration Freezers not only supply commercial catering equipment to the hospitality industry, but we also offer specialist installation services for all of our customers. We can offer the best experienced engineers &amp; store fitters to come and install your commercial refrigeration equipment into your establishment.</p>

<div class="h2"><h2>Our range of Commercial Refrigeration Products</h2></div>

<p>Here at Refrigeration Freezers, we have a wide range of commercial refrigeration products available. Our range of commercial refrigeration products is extensive, you will find everything from commercial <a href="http://www.refrigeration-freezers.com/commercial-refrigeration/display-freezers/3/">freezers</a> and <a href="http://www.refrigeration-freezers.com/commercial-refrigeration/storage-fridges/2/">storage fridges</a>, all the way through to <a href="http://www.refrigeration-freezers.com/commercial-refrigeration/storage-fridges/2/">ice cream displays</a> and specialist catering display units for your commercial establishment - we have it all!</p>

<div class="h2"><h2>Fast Delivery & Best Prices</h2></div>

<p>All commercial refrigeration deliveries to mainland UK, Northern Ireland and the Republic of Ireland are FREE. Not only is our delivery service free, but it is extremely fast also. We make sure every customer at  Refrigeration Freezers has complete customer satisfaction. All of our products are sold with a two year warranty to ensure you peace of mind, and testify of the quality of all of our commercial refrigeration equipment.</p>

<p>In order to be able to supply you with the best prices available, we check and review them on a regular basis, to ensure we remain cheaper than our competitors, although never compromising on the quality of products, as we strive for our customers receive the best offerings possible.</p>

<p>If you would like to know more about our commercial refrigeration equipment, then please <a href="http://www.refrigeration-freezers.com/refrigeration/info/about/contact.cfm"> contact us</a> today for more information.</p>

 
 

